WOT Awards 2025 Red Carpet Stories!

A Night of Style and Substance ✨

The ever-iconic Nisha JamVwal lit up the red carpet with her charisma and wisdom, joining Kaniz Rabbi for a truly enriching conversation. 💫

Nisha shared her thoughts on what it takes to stay relevant year after year — evolving with grace, staying curious, and constantly reinventing yourself while staying true to who you are. 🌟

Her presence was a masterclass in timeless influence — because when elegance meets intellect, relevance becomes effortless. 💖

#WOTAwards2025 #WomenOnTop #WOTRedCarpet #NishaJamVwal

Over the twenty-five years of our #friendship I've seen @laali_dhawan s grace as the silent powerhouse behind her family's achievements. She's the invisible thread weaving through #DavidDhawan s directorial brilliance, @varundvn s meteoric rise as #Bollywood's beloved #hero and @iamrohitdhawan 's creative ventures like the memorable #DesiBoyz 

Her own artistry as an #interiordesigner – most notably transforming #residences – speaks of the talent that flows through them.

During our recent #firesidechat for a #socialservice foundation, I discovered a facet of Lally's philosophy that i conform to as well. 

We explored how true accomplishment isn't always about propelling oneself into the spotlight, but about becoming the foundation upon which loved ones build their dreams. It's a belief that resonates deeply with my own life's rhythm – that sometimes our greatest #victories come from lifting others to their highest potential 

#NishaJamVwal

latestPosts.caption:
How does it matter who does what to themselves to make themselves better ? & make themselves FEEL better?

It’s more important that they felt good about themselves - however they want to work it! Whatever works for them?

Do we really have that much time to sit on judgement and waste a life denigrating people or then instead work on getting a life?

Is it so important to sit on judgement about who took ##Ozempic ? Who wore what? Who did #Botox !? To tear down people? To make calls about why someone introduced someone to someone? 

Can we not look at the bigger picture and focus on improving our game ? Focusing  on #beinghappy and focusing on lifting those around us than always wondering about how to pull people down? 

Remember you’ll be the first to trip and fall should you focus so hard on the downfall of those around you? 

WHEN WE LIFT OTHERS WE RISE!
That’s the name of the game friends !

Lift yourself and those around you, recognizing that everyone carries their own burdens and faces their own challenges and each one is trying to work out an equation called life!

When you step back and see the bigger picture, you realize that life is fundamentally about moving forward and progressing—not dwelling on setbacks of others or their mistakes and ‘wrong’ choices or getting stuck in what holds us back

- its all about  #mutualsupport #sharedstruggles and the importance of #forward #momentum in life! 

#NishaJamVwal

There are moments in life when grandeur meets genuine triumph, and @gautamsinghania99 orchestrated just such an evening with a backdrop of the nautical splendor of a top floor at JK House. We were celebrating Formula 2 driver @kushmainiofficial historic #MonacoGrandPrix #victory – a moment that will forever shimmer in Indian #motorsport history. 

Surrounded by therapeutic blue aquariums where koi fish danced alongside glistening scarlet companions, we toasted the first-ever Formula 2 win by an Indian driver.

#GautamSinghania, with his own racing pedigree from the Ferrari Challenge circuits of Europe and his exquisite collection of vintage automobiles, has been more than a mentor to Maini – he’s been the architect of dreams. 

The evening pulsed with pride, and seeing @nawazbodyartmumbai radiate elegance in her resort ensemble while emanating that distinctive warmth i love her for, reminded me why certain souls simply illuminate the space they grace always

latestPosts.caption:
Reflections In The Aftermath 
#love #values #friendship

Speaking of how sudden life can be
Speaking of how we need to MEND HEAL BRIDGE FORGIVE GIVE SHARE CARE HELP GUIDE MENTOR & DEFINITELY NOT ATTACK OTHERS FOR ANY CHOICES THEY MAKE! LETS NOT PULL DOWN BUT LIFT PEOPLE AROUND US!

Nisha JamVwal

Let’s value, cherish, hold friends dear,
Lets forgive with hearts sincere,
Time passes swift, the years sublime,
Let’s heal all hearts while we have time

As time moves on and years go by,
Let’s mend all bonds before we die

Through depths of care and honest ways,
We’ll face what life may bring,
These bonds will last through all our days,
The joy that friendship brings.

With loyalty that never bends,
And love that knows no end,
Support that lifts us up, 
defends,
Respect that we extend.

Nisha JamVwal

latestPosts.caption:
💫 **Real Talk About Friendship** 💫

Friendship is about wanting to spend time - without some hidden agenda! That's the feeling I had when I was looking forward to spending the evening with my ace activist lawyer friend @abhasinghlawyer who is to me a woman of substance! 💪✨

She's always the first to land up in times of challenge, which it is for me at this moment! Everyone celebrates with you - but the real friends come to your side when your chips are down, isn't it!?

True friendship means showing up - both in joy and in struggle, both in celebration and in support. It's about genuine connection, not convenience. 💕

We were going across to encourage @nataliamistry_ for her first event & despite my circumstances currently, I wanted to be there to applaud Natalia! Because that's what friendship looks like - rising with each  other, especially when it matters most! 🌟

Love to you all & may the #goodtimes roll! ✨

@nishajamvwalnews @nishajamvwal @nishajamvwaluxury

#Friendship #RealFriends #WomenSupportingWomen #Gratitude #ShowingUp #GoodTimes #Tribe #Loyalty #GenuineConnections #NishaJamVwal
